                <mxCell id="rc-inner" value="&lt;b&gt;Rollout Controller Pod&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;image: llm-d-rl:latest (Go binary)&lt;br&gt;port: 8090&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;HTTP API:&lt;br&gt;• POST /v1/generate&lt;br&gt;• POST /v1/weights/init|update&lt;br&gt;• POST /v1/engines/sleep|wake&lt;br&gt;• GET  /v1/pool/status | /v1/health&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;--engine-selector: llm-d.ai/inference-serving=true&lt;br&gt;--router-url: http://llm-d-inference-gateway-istio:80&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;PodWatcher&lt;/b&gt; (pkg/discovery)&lt;br&gt;  Kubernetes informer → EnginePool&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;EnginePool&lt;/b&gt; (pkg/pool)&lt;br&gt;  health checks every 15s" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
