                <mxCell id="epp-inner" value="&lt;b&gt;EPP Pod&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;image: llm-d-inference-scheduler:v0.5.0&lt;br&gt;gRPC port: 9002 (ext_proc)&lt;br&gt;metrics port: 9090&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;--pool-name: llm-d-pool&lt;br&gt;--pool-namespace: llm-d-rl&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Scheduling plugins (epp-config):&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;prefix-cache-scorer&lt;/b&gt; (weight 2×)&lt;br&gt;  → scores by KV-cache prefix hit rate&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;decode-filter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;  → filters high-load pods&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;max-score-picker&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;  → selects highest-scoring pod&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Watches: InferencePool + Pods (RBAC)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
